tag-wrongdoing-al-thulm"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-uM","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":28101,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/23\/fasting-distances-hundred-years\/","url_meta":{"origin":1908,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Allah distances him from Hell by 100 years","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Uqbah ibn Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever fasts a day in the way of Allah Almighty, Allah will distance him from Hell by a measure of one hundred years of travel.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2254 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24550,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/03\/26\/reciters-quran-never-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":1908,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Readers of Quran never enter Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 26, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf the Quran were placed in a leatherskin and then thrown into the fire, it would not burn.\u201d Al-Bayhaqi said, \u201cIt means whoever carries the Quran and recites it will never be touched by Hellfire.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2899,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/16\/allah-not-bless-lucky-charms\/","url_meta":{"origin":1908,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Amulets: Allah will not bless good luck charms","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever hangs an amulet around his neck, Allah will not fulfill his wishes. Whoever hangs a seashell as a charm, Allah will not leave him without penalty. \u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 16951 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":905,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/07\/06\/umar-mercy-pardon-forgiveness\/","url_meta":{"origin":1908,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Forgiveness: No mercy for the unmerciful, unforgiving","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 6, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Qabisah ibn Jabir reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \"Whoever does not show mercy will not receive mercy. Whoever does not forgive others will not be forgiven. Whoever does not pardon others will not be pardoned. Whoever does not protect others will not be protected.\"\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14926,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/11\/daughters-shield-from-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":1908,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Children: His daughters are a shield from Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 11, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever has three daughters and he is patient with them, he provides food and drink for them, and he clothes them, they will be his shield from the Hellfire on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33524,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/16\/good-luck-charms-idolatry\/","url_meta":{"origin":1908,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Amulets: Wearing good luck charms an act of idolatry","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Uqbah ibn \u2018Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, received a group of men and he accepted the pledge of nine of them, while he refrained from one. They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, you accepted the pledge of nine men and left this one\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1908","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadith